        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-03-26 13:28:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n- In oom/kubernetes/policy/charts/pdp/values.yaml, replicaCount should be 3.\n- In oom/kubernetes/policy/charts/pdp/templates/service.yaml, the annotation related to \"serviceName\": \"{{ include \"common.fullname\" . }}-deprecated\" should be removed.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "2f4d5a0547cf2b051da5d058c6fd45837da7faa2",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2887,
          "name": "Ankitkumar Patel",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "ankit@research.att.com",
          "username": "ankit7453"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-03-26 14:07:02.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nIn R2, the policy system will offer static scalability to PDP and thus, PDP replicas should be accessible by PAP using FQDNs derived from PDP charts.\n\nIn oom/kubernetes/policy/resources/config/pe/pap.conf file, should \nPAP_PDP_URL=http://{{ .Release.Name }}-pdp:8081/pdp/\nbe\nPAP_PDP_URL=http://{{pdp-stateful-set-name}}-{replica-#}.{{pdp-service-cluster-name}}:8081/pdp/?",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
